---
import AuroraField from "./AuroraField.astro";
import ProductLayer from "./ProductLayer.astro";
import SystemArchitecture from "./SystemArchitecture.astro";
import SystemInterface from "./SystemInterface.astro";
---

<div class="aurora-page" data-aurora-page data-aurora-field-host>
  <div class="aurora-page__field" aria-hidden="true">
    <AuroraField />
  </div>

  <section class="hero" id="hero" data-aurora-state="hero">
    <div class="hero-shell">
      <p class="hero-kicker">INFRAESTRUCTURA DE DECISIÓN</p>
      <h1>La mente humana tiene un límite. La realidad no.</h1>
      <p class="hero-anchor">Aurora calcula las consecuencias de un movimiento antes de ejecutarlo.</p>
      <div class="hero-body">
        <p>El mercado ya no compite con personas.</p>
        <p>Compite con sistemas.</p>
        <p>El cálculo reemplaza la interpretación.</p>
        <p>Aurora introduce esa capacidad.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/demo" class="cta-link">Someter movimiento a cálculo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contexto" data-aurora-state="context">
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="section-rail">
        <span class="section-kicker">Cambio de estándar</span>
      </div>

      <div class="section-copy section-copy--wide">
        <h2>Hoy es posible ver la estructura de un movimiento antes de actuar.</h2>
        <div class="context-grid">
          <p>La forma de operar cambió. Ya no alcanza con interpretar más rápido ni con agregar más capas humanas sobre la decisión.</p>
          <p>Los movimientos comprometen capital, activan operación y dejan consecuencias. La ventaja ya no es crecer. Es ver la estructura antes de entrar en ella.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="proof" data-aurora-state="proof">
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="section-rail">
        <span class="section-kicker">Prueba</span>
      </div>

      <div class="section-copy section-copy--full">
        <SystemInterface />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="arquitectura" data-aurora-state="architecture">
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="section-rail">
        <span class="section-kicker">Arquitectura y capa de producto</span>
      </div>

      <div class="section-copy section-copy--full">
        <h2>Core. Motores. Superficie operativa.</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Aurora opera como sistema. La web expone la arquitectura y la demo somete un movimiento a cálculo sin duplicar el motor visible.</p>
        <SystemArchitecture />
        <ProductLayer />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cta" id="demo" data-aurora-state="cta">
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="section-rail">
        <span class="section-kicker">Demo</span>
      </div>

      <div class="section-copy section-copy--wide">
        <h2>Pon tu próximo movimiento bajo cálculo.</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Aurora no opina. Calcula.</p>
        <p>La demo prepara el contrato real, registra el movimiento y devuelve lectura, contrafactual e identidad de decisión desde un único adapter.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions hero-actions--section">
          <a href="/demo" class="cta-link">Someter movimiento a cálculo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .aurora-page {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .aurora-page__field {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100svh;
    margin-bottom: -100svh;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .aurora-page > :not(.aurora-page__field) {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero,
  .section {
    position: relative;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: calc(100svh - 80px);
    padding: 110px 24px 120px;
    border-top: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 48% 40%, rgba(214, 255, 234, 0.08), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 13, 16, 0.2), rgba(11, 13, 16, 0.6));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-shell,
  .section-grid {
    width: min(1160px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-shell {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.35rem;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .hero-kicker,
  .section-kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font: 600 11px/1 "Inter", sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-kicker::before,
  .section-kicker::before {
    content: "";
    width: 38px;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(151, 214, 186, 0.48);
  }

  .hero h1,
  .section-copy h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    max-width: 9ch;
    font-size: clamp(50px, 8vw, 92px);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .hero-anchor {
    max-width: 26ch;
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(244, 246, 242, 0.98);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);
    line-height: 1.14;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  .hero-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    max-width: 30ch;
  }

  .hero-body p,
  .section-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-body p {
    color: rgba(225, 229, 220, 0.88);
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.42;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    margin-top: 0.7rem;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 0 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(151, 214, 186, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(151, 214, 186, 0.28);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font: 600 15px/1 "Inter", sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition:
      transform 220ms var(--ease-aurora),
      background 220ms var(--ease-aurora),
      border-color 220ms var(--ease-aurora);
  }

  .cta-link:hover,
  .cta-link:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    background: rgba(151, 214, 186, 0.18);
    border-color: rgba(151, 214, 186, 0.4);
  }

  .section {
    padding: 104px 24px;
  }

  .section-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 190px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 2.6rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .section-copy--wide {
    max-width: 920px;
  }

  .section-copy--full {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .section-copy h2 {
    max-width: 14ch;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px);
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .section-lead {
    max-width: 34ch;
    color: var(--color-text) !important;
    font-size: 22px !important;
    line-height: 1.38 !important;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .context-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.2rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-cta {
    padding-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .hero-actions--section {
    margin-top: 1.3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .section-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-copy h2 {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: 76px 20px 84px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 84px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(42px, 14vw, 62px);
    }

    .hero-anchor {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .hero-body p,
    .section-copy p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .section-lead {
      font-size: 20px !important;
    }

    .context-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
